description: Minimal data models used across the app with JSON helpers for Event, Birthday, Message, and UserProfile classes, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.

classes.name: Event
classes.description: Represents an event with id, title, and dateTime, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.

classes.name: Birthday
classes.description: Represents a birthday with id, name, and date, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.

classes.name: Message
classes.description: Represents a message with id, senderId, text, and sentAt timestamp, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.

classes.name: UserProfile
classes.description: Represents a user profile with uid, displayName, and email, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.
